


These documentation is for Web services Copy Rights to Dtech.com
We have a specific Model Which is extended from Product Model
This model include all data related operation of Web Services

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
We have WS controller which will handle WebService requests 

this controller have the following actions/methods.....


------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
     1 - index(); 
                              // index function operates on based of requested 'record_set' = 'prodcut' or product_catgory
                              //http://dtechsystems.info/service.php/WS?record_set=product   for products
                              //http://dtechsystems.info/service.php/WS?record_set=product_category     for categories



---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
     2 - AllCategories(); 
                              // request to this action will return all categories in DS database in JSON format 
                              //   can make call to this service as (WS/allCategories)
                              // http://dtechsystems.info/service.php/WS/allCategories
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    3  - RequestedCategory($cat_id); 
                              //request to this action will return all products of Requested Category
                              // call this service in this pattern ( WS/allCategories/category_id/55)
                              // http://dtechsystems.info/service.php/WS/allCategories/category_id/55


---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------